  "details": "A vulnerability was determined in BerriAI litellm up to 1.82.2. This affects the function json.dumps of the file litellm/proxy/management_endpoints/ui_sso.py of the component SSO Debug Flow. Executing a manipulation can lead to missing authentication. The attack can be executed remotely. The exploit has been publicly disclosed and may be utilized. The vendor was contacted early about this disclosure.",
